==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Readily
<hw>Read"i*ly</hw> <pr>(r⟦ecr⟧d"⟦icr⟧*l⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>In a ready manner; quickly; promptly.</def>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Without delay or objection; without reluctance;
willingly; cheerfully.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How <qex>readily</qex> we wish time spent revoked!</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Readiness</ent>⟦br⟧
